Description.value: The process of fetching data from Anaplan to create Purchase Requisitions in SAP Ariba ensures seamless integration between planning and procurement. Procurement-related data, such as material details, quantities, and budgets, is extracted from Anaplan via scheduled exports, transformed into the required SAP Ariba format, and transmitted to SAP Ariba, then it processes this data to generate Purchase Requisitions, applying approvals and validations. This integration streamlines procurement, enhances data accuracy, optimizes costs, and ensures compliance with business policies.
